<h1> Password Reset </h1>

<p> To reset your AddVenture password, click the link below. </p>

<%= link_to "Reset password", edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email:@user.email ) %>

<p> This link will expire in two hours. If you have not reset your password in this time, please go back to AddVenture to reset your password again. </p>
</br>
<p> If you did not request this password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will stay as it is now. </p>